value.0: Ritually preserved and animated corpses that maintain their timeless vigil over tombs and temple complexes, Mummies are an effective deterrent to would-be grave-robbers.

Shadows are creatures of living darkness, hating life and light with equal fervor. Their touch leaves the chill of nonexistence, making them very dangerous opponents.
